2025-12-05FIN, MINTRoyal Canadian Mint ActOrder Authorizing the Issue of Two One-dollar Commemorative Circulation Coins Specifying the Characteristics and Determining the Designs (FIFA World Cup 2026) Order authorizing the Royal Canadian Mint to produce two one-dollar commemorative circulation coins marking Canada’s hosting and celebrating Canada’s playing in the 2026 FIFA World Cup.Registration: SOR/2025-0259 Publication Date: 2025-12-17
subject: Order Authorizing the Issue of Two One-dollar Commemorative Circulation Coins Specifying the Characteristics and Determining the Designs (FIFA World Cup 2026)
precis: Order authorizing the Royal Canadian Mint to produce two one-dollar commemorative circulation coins marking Canada’s hosting and celebrating Canada’s playing in the 2026 FIFA World Cup.
